Pre-Requisite : You must have installed unity 5.x on your System
Installation :
-> Download this repository
-> Extract the main zip (Which unzips the other two modules also)
-> Put the extracted repository into a Empty Unity Project folder
-> NOTE : Unity 5.x comes with Standard Assets Folder. Copy that into your project directory to watch this project work! Have fun.
-> For any queries : p.p.amrishkumar@gmail.com
